Name: AccountCurrencyCode
Notes: The currency of the Customer account.

Name: AccountDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer account.

Name: AccountTimeZoneId
Notes: Name of the timezone selected for the Customer account. For example: "(GMT-05:00) Eastern Time". This field does not reflect the current state of daylight saving time for the timezone.

Name: AdGroupId
Notes: The ID of the AdGroup.

Name: AdGroupName
Notes: The name of the AdGroup.

Name: AverageCpc
Notes: The total cost of all clicks divided by the total number of clicks received.

Name: AveragePosition
Notes: Your ad's position relative to those of other advertisers.

Name: CampaignId
Notes: The ID of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignName
Notes: The name of the Campaign.

Name: Clicks
Notes: The number of clicks.

Name: CombinedAdsOrganicClicks
Notes: Clicks from ads or organic search results.

Name: CombinedAdsOrganicClicksPerQuery
Notes: CombinedAdsOrganicClicks divided by CombinedAdsOrganicQueries.

Name: CombinedAdsOrganicQueries
Notes: Total number of searches that returned pages from your site in the organic search results or triggered one of your ads.

Name: Ctr
Notes: The number of clicks your ad receives (Clicks) divided by the number of times your ad is shown (Impressions). Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: CustomerDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer.

Name: Date
Notes: The date formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: ExternalCustomerId
Notes: The Customer ID.

Name: Impressions
Notes: Count of how often your ad has appeared on a search results page or website on the Google Network.

Name: KeywordId
Notes: In the Ad Performance Report this field contains the ID of the criterion that triggered the ad, segmenting the report and preventing zero impressions. The ID can be for any type of criterion, including placements, verticals, etc. Cross-reference with the Criteria Report to determine the criteria type and details.

Name: KeywordTextMatchingQuery
Notes: Keyword that matched the query and triggered the ad.

Name: MatchType
Enum Values:
AUTO / auto
BROAD / broad
BROAD_SESSION / broad (session-based)
EXACT / exact
EXPANDED / broad
PHRASE / phrase
Notes: Match type of the keyword that triggered the ad.

Name: OrganicAveragePosition
Notes: Average top position of your organic listing (or multiple listings) for each query.

Name: OrganicClicks
Notes: Number of times someone clicked your site's listing in the unpaid results for a particular query.

Name: OrganicClicksPerQuery
Notes: Number of clicks youâ€™ve received on your organic search listings divided by the total number of searches that returned pages from your site.

Name: OrganicImpressions
Notes: Number of organic search listing impressions.

Name: OrganicImpressionsPerQuery
Notes: Average number of times a page from your site was listed per query.

Name: OrganicQueries
Notes: Total number of searches that returned organic search results for your site over the given period.

Name: PrimaryCompanyName
Notes: Company name of the account.

Name: SearchQuery
Notes: Query that led to the impression.

Name: SerpType
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ADS_ONLY / Ad shown only
ORGANIC_ONLY / Organic shown only
ADS_AND_ORGANIC / Both shown
Notes: The type of search result.
